## **PART 2: UI COMPONENT LIBRARY 2026**

### **2.1 Core Components**

#### **2.1.1 Glassmorphism Cards**

```jsx
<GlassCard variant="elevated" interactive glow={isActive}>
  <CardHeader>
    <Avatar src={user.avatar} status={user.status} />
    <Typography variant="h3">{user.name}</Typography>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    {children}
  </CardContent>
  <CardFooter>
    <ButtonGroup>
      <Button variant="primary" icon={VideoIcon}>Call</Button>
      <Button variant="secondary" icon={ChatIcon}>Message</Button>
    </ButtonGroup>
  </CardFooter>
</GlassCard>
```

**Styles:**
```css
.glass-card {
  background: rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 24px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
}

.glass-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
}
```

