## **PART 10: SUCCESS METRICS**

### **10.1 Profile KPIs**

| Metric | Target | Measurement |
|--------|--------|-------------|
| Profile Completion Rate | 85% | % of users with >80% complete |
| Profile Views | 100k/month | Total profile views |
| Connection Rate | 30% | % of views that connect |
| Hire Rate | 15% | % of views that hire |
| Profile Edits | 50% | % of users editing monthly |
| Account Deletion Rate | <5% | % of users deleting |
| Reactivation Rate | 20% | % who reactivate during grace |

