## **PART 11: COMPLIANCE & LEGAL**

### **11.1 Data Retention Policy**

```javascript
DATA_RETENTION = {
  active_accounts: 'Until deletion request',
  deleted_accounts: {
    personal_data: '30 days (grace period) then deleted',
    transaction_records: '7 years (legal requirement)',
    tax_documents: '7 years',
    dispute_records: '5 years after resolution',
    analytics: 'Anonymized after 30 days'
  },
  export_requests: 'Stored for 7 days',
  login_history: '90 days',
  messages: 'Deleted with account'
}
```

### **11.2 GDPR/NDPR Compliance**

```
User Rights:
âœ“ Right to access (data export)
âœ“ Right to rectification (edit profile)
âœ“ Right to erasure (delete account)
âœ“ Right to restrict processing (privacy settings)
âœ“ Right to data portability (export)
âœ“ Right to object (opt-out)
âœ“ Rights related to automation (AI preferences)
```

